## Writing Style
- Authoritative and direct — no filler, no hedging
- Senior practitioner tone, not generic consultant language
- Specific about numbers, dates, commercial implications
- Always use named frameworks with ™ symbol
- Never use: "leverage" as verb, "synergies", "circle back"
- Proposals: line-item methodology licenses separately from advisory fees

## Code Style
- PowerShell: Write-Ok/Write-Fail/Write-Step helper pattern
- JavaScript: async/await only
- HTML/CSS: CSS custom properties, dark theme (#0a0a0a base)
- Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (display) + DM Sans (body)
- Brand colors: --gold: #c9a96e | --ink: #0a0a0a | --chalk: #e8e4dc
